-- Berlin’s New Airport Opening Is Delayed Until 2013, Bild Reports
-- B y   S h e e n a g h   M a t t h e w s
-- 2012-05-16T05:19:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-16/berlin-s-new-airport-opening-is-delayed-until-2013-bild-reports.html
The opening of Berlin’s new airport
will be delayed until spring 2013,  Bild reported , citing a
letter from the building authorities in Koenigs Wusterhausen
district.  Authorities are demanding “fully automatic operations,”
which can only be assured at the beginning of 2013, the German
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sheenagh Matthews in Frankfurt at 
 smatthews6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
